{"word":"συμμαχίς","slug":"συμμαχίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμμαχίς</b></el> <el>(συμμᾰχίς, ίδος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> of <a href='S:σύμμαχος'><el>σύμμαχος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>allied</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>ξ. πόλις</el> <i>an allied</i> state, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; also <el>ἡ ς.</el> (without <el>πόλις</el>) <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <el>τὸ ξυμμαχικόν</el>, <i>the body of allies</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}